This package distributes AutoUI-generated Vue 3 component primitives. The
generated visual layer is derived from the projects listed below; their
licenses (all MIT) are acknowledged here.

================================================================================
reka-ui
https://reka-ui.com
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
License: MIT
Copyright (c) Radix Vue / reka-ui contributors

The behavior layer (accessibility, keyboard navigation, focus management) of
every generated component is built on top of reka-ui primitives, imported at
runtime via `import { ... } from 'reka-ui'`. reka-ui is declared as a (optional)
peer dependency.

================================================================================
shadcn-vue
https://www.shadcn-vue.com
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
License: MIT
Copyright (c) shadcn-vue contributors

The Tailwind CSS class recipes ("visual layer") emitted into each generated
`.vue` file are derived from the shadcn-vue reference implementation. Per the
shadcn-vue model, components are copied into the consumer's project and owned
by the consumer. Attribution is preserved in this file and in a header comment
atop each generated `.vue`.

================================================================================
Tailwind CSS
https://tailwindcss.com
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
License: MIT
Copyright (c) Adam Wathan, Jonathan Reinink, and Tailwind CSS contributors

Utility class names referenced by the generated components are part of the
Tailwind CSS vocabulary. A precompiled `dist/styles.css` is offered for
zero-config consumers.
